reviewText: My son loves this show, and honestly so do I.  I know some people have complained to me about thinking that Chicas kazoo voice can be irritating, but I think it goes with the imagination theme of the show and helps young children  learn language from context clues.  I haven't watched this dvd yet because it's going to be an easter gift, but I'm sure it won't disappoint.
